The paper discusses vulnerability analysis in software systems, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the use of automated systems and tools, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE). The proposed approach of human-assisted tool-centered paradigm involves the use of artificial intelligence techniques, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The implementation of the proposed system involves programming languages and compilers, which falls under the category of programming languages (cs.PL). Finally, the proposed system involves the orchestration of automated and human-assisted systems, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY).
